{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c36c0c408d","title":"争取战机迅速完成战役部署","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0c4356f112","index":0,"year":1950,"month":10,"day":21,"articleId":"c36c0c408d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"3a47aa2586","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"c36c0c408d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓华，当时任中国人民志愿军第十三兵团司令员兼政治委员。"},{"id":"8e6b5bcbcb","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"c36c0c408d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭，指彭德怀，当时任中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员。安东，旧市名，即今辽宁丹东。14]高，指高岗，当时任东北军区司令员兼政治委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f78d371046","type":"title","text":"争取战机迅速完成战役部署","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"c36c0c408d"},{"id":"3a47aa2586","type":"paragraph","text":"邓华同志，并告彭及高","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"c36c0c408d"},{"id":"8e6b5bcbcb","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）你们是否已前进，我意十三兵团部应即去彭德怀同志所在之地点和彭住在一起并改组为中国人民志愿军司令部，以便部署作战。现在是争取战机问题，是在几天之内完成战役部署以便几天之后开始作战的问题，而不是先有一个时期部署防御然后再谈攻击的问题。（二）如部队渡河须有机构在安东指挥，则可留适当同志率一部机构留在安东，你和其余同志率必要机构即往彭处为宜，望豹定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"c36c0c408d"},{"id":"e47cc23591","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"c36c0c408d"},{"id":"b264c74bb2","type":"paragraph","text":"十月二十一日三时半","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"c36c0c408d"}],"page":{"id":"b1bb18c5d7","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"c36c0c408d","start":263,"end":263}}}},"__N_SSG":true}